54:["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/80 leading-relaxed","children":["Gartner's landmark 2026 forecast predicts that by 2027, ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"half of all companies that reduced customer service headcount due to AI will be forced to rehire staff"}]," to maintain service quality. Only 20% of layoffs were directly attributable to AI; most were driven by economic pressures. Gartner VP Analyst Kathy Ross notes: \"AI can handle simple, repetitive tasks, but it cannot replicate the expertise, empathy, and judgment that human agents provide\" (Gartner, 2026)."]}]
